{"tid":896481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【歡場風波】尖沙咀24歲女應徵文員變陪坐 唔肯「出街」遭客圍毆","createTime":"2018-11-10T05:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T05:46:53.000Z","uid":52490,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab73e310747468d7527b37f09439e783cdeec728","tid":896481,"uid":52490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"昨（9日）深夜11時許，警方接獲一名姓梁（24歲）女子報案，指自己於尖沙咀山林道4號一間夜總會內，因事與三名男顧客發生爭執，並遭對方打傷頭部，三人逞兇後逃去無蹤。救護員趕抵將梁女送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，女事主原本應徵「文員」，昨為首日開工，但被職員遊說落場坐檯做小姐「陪坐」，事發時因不肯「出街」而遭客人毆打。警方調查後將案件列作「襲擊」處理，正追緝三名男子歸案。"},{"pid":"44c1f58633e05526d5f4b0537db591657f84402f","tid":896481,"uid":52490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/尖沙咀24歲女應徵文員變陪坐-唔肯-出街-被客人圍毆-190900683.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%92%8024%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E6%87%89%E5%BE%B5%E6%96%87%E5%93%A1%E8%AE%8A%E9%99%AA%E5%9D%90-%E5%94%94%E8%82%AF-%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%97-%E8%A2%AB%E5%AE%A2%E4%BA%BA%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86-190900683.html&d=gKsu5e2IlVg3nxeHSNKNb%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=dadeb653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/尖沙咀24歲女應徵文員變陪坐-唔肯-出街-被客人圍毆-190900683.html</a>"},{"pid":"31102b65f4d636d21618b656711813284fc13841","tid":896481,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:27:40.000Z","msg":"咩年代 仲有人中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e7ee371b7667060d9003f5276354a089563ddf","tid":896481,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:30:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"816378a03a6509e40f224e48ac6c228fa2028a28","tid":896481,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:32:33.000Z","msg":"天天出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d360e1cff747b913391f5c20ca2303edcdd5210c",